{
  "text": "In the following set of experiments, we compare MMO-CC with three DG-based CC algorithms, namely, DECC-DG [CITATION_1] , CBCC1-DG [CITATION_2] , and CBCC2-DG [CITATION_3] , and one GDGbased CC algorithm, i.e., CC-GDG-CMAES [CITATION_4] . To further challenge the performance of the MMO-CC, ideal grouping (IG) is considered and the resultant DECC-IG [CITATION_5] and CC-IG-CMAES [CITATION_6] are also compared with MMO-CC.",
  "correct_citation": {
